title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 05.21.08
description:
#1 DAD OR #1 SUSPECT:
    ---------------------
    Christina and Jason are no longer in a relationship, but have two little girls together. Christina claims that her 2 1/2 year old comes home from Jason&#039;s house claiming he has touched her in a sexual manner. Jason has denied this accusation from the get-go and has even passed a lie detector test given by the police department. So why does this young child keeping accusing her dad of such a vulgar thing?! Is he responsible? Or has Christina been coaching her in order to get revenge on Jason? Steve goes head to head with both parents to find out who is to blame.
